# GitHub-native CODEOWNERS — auto-requests review from the matching
# owner(s) when a PR touches the listed paths. Last-match-wins,
# mirroring how GitHub evaluates the file.
#
# Distinct from `.github/OWNERS` (used by the custom pr-welcome-comment
# workflow). Keep both in sync when adding new areas.
#
# Syntax: <pattern> <@owner> [@other ...]
#   * a leading `/` anchors to the repo root
#   * a trailing `/` matches a directory
#   * `*` matches anything except `/`
#   * `**` matches anything

